{"type":"message","id":"56dce8d0","parentId":"18d5a296","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:11:12.915Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has started a new session. According to AGENTS.md, I need to:\n1. Read SOUL.md — this is who I am\n2. Read USER.md — this is who I'm helping\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. If in MAIN SESSION (direct chat with human): Also read MEMORY.md\n\nLet me check what files exist and read them. The current date is 2026-03-20, so I should check memory/2026-03-20.md and memory/2026-03-19.md.\n\nFrom the project context already loaded, I can see:\n- SOUL.md: I'm 狐狸 (Fox), a PPT assistant/presentation expert\n- USER.md: The user is 小王子 (Little Prince) from planet B612\n- MEMORY.md: Contains some memories about the user\n\nLet me check if there are any memory files for today or yesterday.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_241bfff72aaf41c0808f865f","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-20.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_46f8954596bd48ba8c90c0c3","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-19.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773997867052}}
{"type":"message","id":"3b6500f2","parentId":"56dce8d0","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:11:13.013Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_241bfff72aaf41c0808f865f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-20 - 第一天\n\n## 对话开始\n\n用户通过 webchat 联系了我。这是我们的第一次对话。\n\n用户说：\"你好\"\n\n我正在按照 BOOTSTRAP.md 的指示进行初始化。\n\n## 下一步\n\n根据 BOOTSTRAP.md：\n1. 进行对话，了解彼此\n2. 填写 IDENTITY.md 和 USER.md\n3. 讨论 SOUL.md 的内容\n4. 删除 BOOTSTRAP.md\n\n## 对话记录\n\n- 15:04 用户说\"你好\"\n- 15:05 用户再次说\"你好\"（可能是在测试或等待回应）\n- 15:21 用户说\"猜猜我是谁\"\n\n## 时间\n\n- 会话开始时间：2026-03-20 15:04 GMT+8\n- 时区：Asia/Shanghai"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773997873007}}
